  div.normal.designer
    h1 Genuina Market
    img.designer(src="/staticRev/images/genuinaMarket.png" alt="Genuina Market")
    p Every piece created by an artisan tells a unique story that has been handed down from one generation to the other. When you shop at Genuina you contribute to the preservation of ancestral traditions; you are taking stories directly to your home and wardrobe.
    p We expertise in Mexican culture since is one of the richest and most colorful cultures in the world, plus it is also where our home and heart resides.
    p But we also have the pleasure to display artwork from artists worldwide and to showcase our collaborations with India, Turkey, Guatemala, Chile and many more magic places! We live for culture, color and tradition! 
